// first fold
.wrapper
  .container
    .section.mtop2
      // New listing Form
      form#newListing
        .row
          .col-md-6
            .form-group
              label(for='Title') Title
              input#title.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Title of your listing')
            .form-group
              label(for='listingDesc') Listing Description
              input#listingDesc.form-control.longInput(type='text', placeholder='Describe your listing details')
              br
              | Hint: Some hint about the description.
            .Rectangle-51
              .box__input
                i.fa.fa-camera-retro.fa-3.camera-icon(aria-hidden='true')
                label(for='file')
                  span.box__dragndrop
                span.box__button(type='submit') Upload image of your ticket
                br
                p
                  span.box__uploading Uploadingâ€¦
                  span.box__success Done!
                  span.box__error Error!
          .col-md-6
            .form-group
              label(for='Venue') Venue
              input#Venue.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Name of venue the event takes place')
          .col-md-4
            .form-group
              label(for='Price') Price
              input#Price.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Price per ticket in US dollars')
              | Describe your listing details
          .col-md-2
            .form-group
              label(for='Quantity') Quantity
              input#Quantity.form-control(style='display:inline-block;', type='text', placeholder='Number')
          .col-md-6
            .form-group
              label(for='Event') Event
              input#Event.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Name of event ie. Justin Bieber @ TheVenue Feb 1st')
              br
              | Hint: Ticketsloth will suggest event names as you type.
            a#legend.vermillion(href='#') Can't find your event?
        .col-md-6
          button.btn.btn-custom.mtop2(type='submit') CONFIRM AND SUBMIT
